      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Helen Wright Papers consist primarily of correspondence written to Wright by her piano teachers Myra Hess (1890-1965) and Teresa Carreño (1853-1917). The Papers also contain signed photographs of Hess and Carreño, newspaper clippings, and miscellaneous items.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
